# Design System Patterns

## Color Usage

Always use design tokens from `globals.css` instead of hardcoded colors:

- ✅ `bg-primary` / `text-primary-foreground`
- ✅ `bg-secondary` / `text-secondary-foreground` (background color)
- ✅ `bg-secondary-green` / `text-secondary-green-foreground` (active status)
- ✅ `bg-tertiary` / `text-tertiary-foreground` (in-progress status)
- ✅ `bg-accent` / `text-accent-foreground`
- ✅ `bg-destructive` / `text-destructive-foreground`
- ✅ `bg-muted` / `text-muted-foreground`
- ❌ `bg-[#1a73e8]` or `text-gray-400`
- Note: Frist (deadline) colors are hardcoded in `useDueBgStyle()` hook, not using CSS variables

## Button Hierarchy

Follow this button hierarchy:

1. **Primary** (`variant="default"`) - Main action on page
2. **Secondary** (`variant="secondary"`) - Alternative action
3. **Outline** (`variant="outline"`) - Less important action
4. **Ghost** (`variant="ghost"`) - Subtle/toolbar action
5. **Destructive** (`variant="destructive"`) - Delete/remove actions
6. **Link** (`variant="link"`) - Navigation links

## Badge Colors

Use semantic colors for status badges. All badges use low-opacity backgrounds with matching text colors for better contrast.

### Badge Variants

- `variant="default"` - Primary color (`bg-primary/10 text-primary`) - Used for "Ny" status
- `variant="primary"` - Chart 2 color (`bg-chart-2/20 text-chart-2`) - Used for "Vunnet" status
- `variant="secondary"` - Secondary green (`bg-secondary-green/10 text-secondary-green`) - Used for "Aktiv lead"
- `variant="tertiary"` - Tertiary orange (`bg-tertiary/20 text-tertiary`) - Used for "Under arbeid" status
- `variant="destructive"` - Destructive red (`bg-destructive/10 text-destructive`) - Used for "Tapt" status
- `variant="outline"` - Border only, transparent background
- `variant="bortfalt"` - Muted color (`bg-muted/60 text-muted-foreground`) - Used for "Bortfalt" status

### Status Badges (Lead Statuses)

- **NEW**: `variant="default"` (primary color)
- **IN_PROGRESS**: `variant="tertiary"` (orange)
- **WON**: `variant="primary"` (chart-2/turquoise)
- **LOST**: `variant="destructive"` (red)
- **BORTFALT**: `variant="bortfalt"` (muted)
- **Aktiv lead**: `variant="secondary"` (green)

### Activity Log Badges

- **Oppfølging**: `variant="secondary"` (green)
- **Kommentar**: `variant="default"` (primary, no variant specified)
- **E-post**: `variant="primary"` (turquoise)

## Spacing

Use Tailwind spacing scale consistently:

- `gap-2` (8px) for small gaps
- `gap-4` (16px) for standard gaps
- `p-4` (16px) for standard padding
- `p-6` (24px) for larger padding

## Typography

- Headings: `text-lg font-semibold` or `text-xl font-semibold`
- Body: `text-sm` or `text-base`
- Muted text: `text-muted-foreground`
- Labels: `text-sm font-medium`

